title: Ti-10V-2Fe-3Al
text: Ti-10V-2Fe-3Al (UNS designation R56410), also known as Ti 10-2-3, is a <a href="Non-ferrous%20metal">non-ferrous</a> near-beta <a href="titanium%20alloy">titanium alloy</a> featuring an excellent combination of strength, <a href="ductility">ductility</a>, fracture toughness and high cycle fatigue strength. It is typically used in the <a href="aerospace%20industry">aerospace industry</a> for critical aircraft structures, such as landing gear.
